{"tid":139741,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"遊戲係IT產業定文化產業？","createTime":"2017-03-01T15:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T16:06:37.000Z","uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea80595941f102dc9871daa0cf6a2902138b9f6","tid":139741,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"稻船敬二曾經係NHK節目&mdash;&mdash;世界遊戲革命到講過：<br />\n僅憑遊戲本身是不行的，要與日本動畫這個被世界認可的東西形成一體<br />\n<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNDk3Nzg4MjQ0.html?spm=a2h1n.8261147.0.0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.youku.com%2Fv_show%2Fid_XNDk3Nzg4MjQ0.html%3Fspm%3Da2h1n.8261147.0.0&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e16f34de\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNDk3Nzg4MjQ0.html?spm=a2h1n.8261147.0.0</a><br />\n14:53<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係Crytek CEO又講過以下既說話<br />\n       &ldquo;在現任主機上，沒有任何一款遊戲竭盡全能後能在技術上做得能比crysis 3更好。大多數遊戲甚至在技術上無法接近crysis 2。我並非在討論藝術風格&mdash;&mdash;藝術是主觀的&mdash;&mdash;但純粹的事實就是我們的crysis 2已經幾乎耗盡了Xbox 360和PS3的機能，直到今天我還沒看到一款遊戲能夠達到這種地步。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n       他繼續說道：&ldquo;隨便哪天我都可以用任何方式對抗戰爭機器或Halo，我們所投入的資料總量和細節程度遠遠高於它們。而隨著crysis 3的到來，我們將其推到了一個新的高度，當然PC版還要再高兩個檔次。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n英文原文：<a href=\"https://www.videogamer.com/news/crysis-3-maxes-out-consoles-says-crytek-ceo-not-even-1-left\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.videogamer.com%2Fnews%2Fcrysis-3-maxes-out-consoles-says-crytek-ceo-not-even-1-left&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f6de15cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.videogamer.com/news/crysis-3-maxes-out-consoles-says-crytek-ceo-not-even-1-left</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個人推銷遊戲既方法好唔同，稻船就話要同動畫結合，Crytek CEO就話以技術對抗對手。一個講法似係文化產業而另一個講法就似IT產業。<br />\n大家覺得邊個方法有用D？同埋遊戲係IT產業定文化產業？"},{"pid":"a2cdae633c5a43c93c65431bc6f4e5e256cde55a","tid":139741,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"遊戲係娛樂產業  只係娛樂都屬於一種文化 你強行叫佢做文化產業都可以既"},{"pid":"711bcd0298356c43f721ec18694aafceb5203757","tid":139741,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m133eg2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm133eg2.png&h=d3f0c9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XLj709.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XLj709.png&h=0c3f93a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0b9007d52b7f867ef7ca41601a571c086ea5a17","tid":139741,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:06:37.000Z","msg":"稻船"}]}